==English==

===Pronunciation===
IPA: ˈmʌn.i

===Noun===
'''money''' ([[mass noun]])
#Some [[currency]].
#Hard [[cash]], as opposed to cheques or [[credit]] cards.
#Assets such as houses or cars which show you have money.
#Richness, rich people-particularly those who didn't inherit it.
#A person who funds an operation.

